<br />
May 3, 2112's day of the week: Tuesday.<br />
May 3, 2112 - 577 days = October 4, 2110.<br />
October 4, 2110 - 50 years, 6 months, 30 weeks and 30 days = August 6, 2059<br />
August 6, 2059 - 500 years, 18 months, 6 weeks and 1 day = December 24, 1557<br />
<br />
Take the first letter of everything above that the interviewer was requesting (Tuesday, October, August, December) and you get TOAD.